@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_avevmx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.29)))
    v2 = 0.41
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.51)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = 0.58
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.24 + v2 + 1.00)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.14 - tmp + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
